<B><font face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='2'>SAYANARA SUCKERS!<BR></B></font><font face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='1'>2003-05-09 02:20:24&nbsp;-&nbsp;<font face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif' size='1'><I>Furor Planedefiler</I>&nbsp;	</td>
  </tr>
